!! Automatic Updates

Automatically update caches for authoring at the scheduled hour and minute.

* If **Hour** is set to `-1`, the update will run **every hour**.
* If **Minute** is set to `-1`, the update will run **every minute**.
* If both are `-1`, the update will run **every minute of every hour**.

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/auto-update/enable" field="text" checked="enable" unchecked="disable" default="disable">
  <$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/auto-update/enable">Enable Automatic Updates</$link>
</$checkbox>

* Hour: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/auto-update/hour" default="-1" tag="input" />
* Minute: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/auto-update/minute" default="-1" tag="input" />

